# path-comment-hook

```
    /·\
   /│·│\    ┌─┐┌─┐┬ ┬
  / │·│ \   ├─┘│  ├─┤
 /  │·│  >  ┴  └─┘┴ ┴
/___│·│___\ path-comment-hook
```

